      </div><h3 class="sub-h4 mt-[40px] normal-case">How it feels</h3><div class="mt-2 rte"><div class="metafield-rich_text_field"><p>A whipped airy cream that feels smooth and lightweight with a matte finish. Recommended for normal, combination, oily or sensitive skin.</p></div></div><h3 class="sub-h4 mt-[40px] normal-case">Why we made it</h3><div class="mt-2 rte"><div class="metafield-rich_text_field"><p>Mattescreen was created as a daily sunscreen option for those with normal to oily skin, and recommended even for sensitive skin. Its tinted, blendable formula is designed to mattify and smooth skin&#39;s appearance while visibly blurring pores and minimizing white cast. Mattescreen is free of pore-clogging oils and provides expert SPF 40 sun protection. </p></div></div></div>

