    <div id="yotpo-reviews-section-data" style="margin-top:4px; font-size:11px; line-height:1.35; color:#555; max-height:220px; overflow:auto; padding:6px 8px; border:1px solid #eee; border-radius:4px; background:#fafafa;">   <section id="yotpo-reviews-overall-rating">     <p><strong>Overall rating:</strong> 4.6650248 / 5 from 1624 reviews.</p>   </section>   <section id="yotpo-reviews-ai-summary">     <h3>AI Generated Review Summary</h3>     <p>The Mineral Mattescreen SPF 40 is a mineral, mattifying tinted sunscreen that visibly blurs pores and smooths the skin's appearance. It provides skincare benefits, offers great sun protection with a lightweight, invisible finish, and has a silky, smooth finish that blends well with the skin tone. Customers appreciate its perfect coverage and non-greasy feeling, though opinions on the tint and skin feel vary.</p>   </section>   <section id="yotpo-reviews-summary-topics">     <h3>Summary topics</h3>     <ul>       <li><span class="yotpo-topic-name">Feels</span>: <span class="yotpo-topic-coverage">15%</span></li><li><span class="yotpo-topic-name">Sun Protection</span>: <span class="yotpo-topic-coverage">5%</span></li><li><span class="yotpo-topic-name">Coverage</span>: <span class="yotpo-topic-coverage">10%</span></li><li><span class="yotpo-topic-name">Look</span>: <span class="yotpo-topic-coverage">12%</span></li><li><span class="yotpo-topic-name">Finish</span>: <span class="yotpo-topic-coverage">10%</span></li>     </ul>   </section>   <section id="yotpo-reviews-review-topics">     <p><strong>Review topics:</strong> [&quot;size&quot;,&quot;absorbs&quot;,&quot;results&quot;,&quot;fit&quot;,&quot;color&quot;,&quot;ingredients&quot;,&quot;irritation&quot;,&quot;issues&quot;,&quot;weight&quot;,&quot;smell&quot;,&quot;quality&quot;,&quot;price&quot;,&quot;spots&quot;,&quot;feels&quot;,&quot;texture&quot;,&quot;shipping&quot;,&quot;packaging&quot;,&quot;formula&quot;,&quot;skin&quot;,&quot;works&quot;,&quot;look&quot;,&quot;amount&quot;,&quot;glow&quot;,&quot;use&quot;,&quot;coverage&quot;,&quot;protection&quot;,&quot;face&quot;,&quot;lines&quot;,&quot;pores&quot;,&quot;shade&quot;].</p>   </section>   <section id="yotpo-reviews-highlights">     <h3>Review highlights</h3>     <ul>       <li><span class="yotpo-highlight-text">&quot;It protects skin well, doesn&rsquo;t irritate, has a great tint, doesn&rsquo;t cause breakouts, doesn&rsquo;t leave a shine.&quot;</span> &mdash; <span class="yotpo-highlight-author">Arayoan V.</span></li><li><span class="yotpo-highlight-text">&quot;I wear this daily, it&rsquo;s a smooth silky matte finish that makes your skin look good.&quot;</span> &mdash; <span class="yotpo-highlight-author">Carol P.</span></li><li><span class="yotpo-highlight-text">&quot;My face is normally shiny and prone to breakouts and it makes my skin look amazing and is long lasting.&quot;</span> &mdash; <span class="yotpo-highlight-author">Sw</span></li>     </ul>   </section>   <section id="yotpo-reviews-individual-reviews">     <h3>Reviews</h3>     <article class="yotpo-review" data-reviewer="Rachel" data-rating="4">       <h4 class="yotpo-review-title">Great suncreen, maddening packaging</h4>       <p class="yotpo-review-body">&quot;I have very sensitive skin, and I love this sunscreen. Finally - a mineral sunblock that's lightweight with a pleasant, powder-like smoothness instead of something thick and greasy with a strong white cast. The tint is minimal, but not nonexistent, and the matte effect is gentle. However, I HATE the shape of the bottle. It is very obviously - by the design orientation and the advertising - supposed to be upright, stood up on the cap. However, the cap is too rounded on the rim and far, far too narrow. It tips over CONSTANTLY and is difficult to store as intended. There is absolutely no excuse for it. Supergoop: y'all gotta fix this ASAP.&quot;</p>       <p class="yotpo-review-author">&mdash; <span class="yotpo-reviewer-name">Rachel</span> (<span class="yotpo-review-rating">4/5</span>)</p>     </article><article class="yotpo-review" data-reviewer="Hil" data-rating="5">       <h4 class="yotpo-review-title">Nice lightly tinted matte sunscreen</h4>       <p class="yotpo-review-body">&quot;The texture and tint are perfect for everyday wear. I usually wear this daily when working in the office. Work great with the translucent powder for quick and easy protection with a it of color correction.&quot;</p>       <p class="yotpo-review-author">&mdash; <span class="yotpo-reviewer-name">Hil</span> (<span class="yotpo-review-rating">5/5</span>)</p>     </article><article class="yotpo-review" data-reviewer="Amanda" data-rating="5">       <h4 class="yotpo-review-title">This changed my life!</h4>       <p class="yotpo-review-body">&quot;I have been using sunscreen on my face for years. Learned it from both my grandma and mom. I love a minimal make-up look and was using nothing tinted for years. Then decided to try this, and woah- it just creates a beautiful effect on my skin- poreless, longlasting, doesn't break me out, and of course, the best part: super sun protection. And this is from someone who has acne prone skin! Highliy recommend.&quot;</p>       <p class="yotpo-review-author">&mdash; <span class="yotpo-reviewer-name">Amanda</span> (<span class="yotpo-review-rating">5/5</span>)</p>     </article><article class="yotpo-review" data-reviewer="Julie" data-rating="1">       <h4 class="yotpo-review-title">New Formula is NOT the Same</h4>       <p class="yotpo-review-body">&quot;This has been my go-to for YEARS but the reformulation is awful - the &quot;original, which they're calling Sunrise, is extremely pigmented and orange. Looks absolutely awful.   Back to the search for an HG sunscreen. . .&quot;</p>       <p class="yotpo-review-author">&mdash; <span class="yotpo-reviewer-name">Julie</span> (<span class="yotpo-review-rating">1/5</span>)</p>     </article><article class="yotpo-review" data-reviewer="Jennifer Y." data-rating="5">       <h4 class="yotpo-review-title">LOVE this Mineral Mattescreen</h4>       <p class="yotpo-review-body">&quot;First tried this from a sample I received with my usual order of Glowscreen and Bright Eyes. I get SO many compliments on my (literally) glowing skin, but really wanted to find something that was more matte for other occasions (and I no longer do foundation). Exactly what I was looking for was delivered in a sample of Supergoop Mattescreen and it was immediately added to my rotation. It is light, it is matte, it is exactly what I needed. Gives me some light coverage with a beautiful matte finish and I LOVE it. Nailed it again, Supergoop!&quot;</p>       <p class="yotpo-review-author">&mdash; <span class="yotpo-reviewer-name">Jennifer Y.</span> (<span class="yotpo-review-rating">5/5</span>)</p>     </article><article class="yotpo-review" data-reviewer="Julie R." data-rating="5">       <h4 class="yotpo-review-title">Easy &quot;to go&quot; routine</h4>       <p class="yotpo-review-body">&quot;Tinted sunscreen that doesn't irritate my face? Where have you been all my life? This and mascara and I'm ready for summer fun!&quot;</p>       <p class="yotpo-review-author">&mdash; <span class="yotpo-reviewer-name">Julie R.</span> (<span class="yotpo-review-rating">5/5</span>)</p>     </article><article class="yotpo-review" data-reviewer="Terri L." data-rating="5">       <h4 class="yotpo-review-title">Perfect</h4>       <p class="yotpo-review-body">&quot;I&rsquo;ve used the universal shade before but was especially intrigued when I noticed it now comes in various shades. Ordered golden hour and am very pleased with the look!!&quot;</p>       <p class="yotpo-review-author">&mdash; <span class="yotpo-reviewer-name">Terri L.</span> (<span class="yotpo-review-rating">5/5</span>)</p>     </article><article class="yotpo-review" data-reviewer="Tracey S." data-rating="2">       <h4 class="yotpo-review-title">Beautiful finish, but breaks me out</h4>       <p class="yotpo-review-body">&quot;This sunscreen really does look and feel gorgeous, but after 2 days of use I started to get tons of blackheads and bumps. What a shame, will be looking for something else.&quot;</p>       <p class="yotpo-review-author">&mdash; <span class="yotpo-reviewer-name">Tracey S.</span> (<span class="yotpo-review-rating">2/5</span>)</p>     </article><article class="yotpo-review" data-reviewer="Barbara C." data-rating="5">       <h4 class="yotpo-review-title">Great natural look</h4>       <p class="yotpo-review-body">&quot;Was worried when I first started to apply it, as it looked a bit chalky. But then it blends in to the skin perfectly. Very natural look and keeps skin from looking oily all day. This is my new go to.&quot;</p>       <p class="yotpo-review-author">&mdash; <span class="yotpo-reviewer-name">Barbara C.</span> (<span class="yotpo-review-rating">5/5</span>)</p>     </article><article class="yotpo-review" data-reviewer="Barbara T." data-rating="5">       <h4 class="yotpo-review-title">Like silk!</h4>       <p class="yotpo-review-body">&quot;I like this even more than I thought that I would. It goes on like a silky butter, and it doesn't leave any evidence that it is a mineral formula. I would definitely buy this again.&quot;</p>       <p class="yotpo-review-author">&mdash; <span class="yotpo-reviewer-name">Barbara T.</span> (<span class="yotpo-review-rating">5/5</span>)</p>     </article>   </section>   <section id="yotpo-reviews-qa">     <h3>Q&amp;A</h3>     <dl>       <dt class="yotpo-qa-question">Does this product have a fragrance or scent?</dt><dd class="yotpo-qa-answer">Hi Michelle,  All our formulas are synthetic fragrance free. Natural extracts are sometimes used to add a light refreshing scent like in our PLAY Everyday Day Lotion with Sunflower Extract. Certain ingredients used in sunscreen formulations have a natural scent that may not only come from the sunscreen active themselves. Once it is lathered on to the skin any scent natural to the formulation will dissipate completely.</dd><dt class="yotpo-qa-question">Hi I had purchased this product recently. But it does not clearly stated whether it is using Non nano zinc or Nano Zinc. Could you please kindly verify and revert with which zinc it is using? Many thanks. ~ Akemi</dt><dd class="yotpo-qa-answer">Hi there,  All our 100% Mineral formulas are non-nano! 🔆</dd><dt class="yotpo-qa-question">Is this too dark for fair skin? Currently, I use the mineral unseen sunscreen. Should I stick with that?</dt><dd class="yotpo-qa-answer">Hi there,  Mineral Unseen is non-tinted, so I&amp;#x27;d recommend sticking with that if Mattescreen is too dark. If you&amp;#x27;d like to try a different tinted option we do have our Protec(tint) Daily Skin Tint, which comes in 14 flexible shades. If you need further assistance, please reach out to hello@supergoop.com! 💛</dd><dt class="yotpo-qa-question">Hi! Is the zinc used coated or uncoated?</dt><dd class="yotpo-qa-answer">Hi Angelica,  The zinc used is coated! 🙂</dd><dt class="yotpo-qa-question">Does this sunscreen use nano-zinc?</dt><dd class="yotpo-qa-answer">Hi Isa,  Yes, this product is non-nano! 🔆</dd>     </dl>   </section> </div>
  



